Market News  21 AM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Smartsheet Inc Sees IPO Of 11.6 Million Shares Priced To Be Between $10 And $12 Per Share – SEC Filing Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
  Smartsheet Inc: 
* SMARTSHEET INC SEES IPO OF 11.6 MILLION SHARES PRICED TO BE BETWEEN $10 AND $12 PER SHARE – SEC FILING 
* SMARTSHEET SAYS CO IS OFFERING 10 MILLION SHARES OF CLASS A COMMON STOCK, SELLING SHAREHOLDERS ARE OFFERING 1.6 MILLION SHARES OF CO'S CLASS A COMMON STOCK Source text: ( bit.ly/2HnLVKr ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
